column2: Gores Holdings IV Inc. is a blank check company. The Company is formed for the purpose of effecting a merger, capital stock exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, reorganization or similar business combination with one or more businesses. The Company has not identified any potential business combination target and is focused on pursuing an acquisition opportunity in any business industry or sector. The Company is focused on identifying, acquiring and managing businesses in diverse sectors, including industrials, technology, telecommunications, media and entertainment, business services, healthcare and consumer products.
